## Summary

- [bold]Base Stat[/bold] — immutable, starting value
- [bold]Modifiers[/bold] — temporary bonuses from spells, items, buffs
- [bold]Effective Stat[/bold] — base + sum of modifiers (capped at 10)
- [bold]Tracking[/bold] — each modifier source is recorded
- [bold]Overflow[/bold] — excess beyond cap becomes available points
- [bold]Syncing[/bold] — AutoNetworkedField keeps clients in sync

This system powers all stat bonuses in OpenEdge 14!
